    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sticky sweet chilli</strong> <strong>lean</strong> <strong>pork</strong> with <strong>basmati</strong> <strong>rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped coriander</strong>,<strong> remaining sliced spring onion </strong>and a<strong> lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
